'''本地治里機場'''（{{lang-en|'''Puducherry Airport'''}}，{{airport codes|PNY|VOPC}}）是一個位於[[印度|印度]][[中央直辖区|中央直辖区]][[本地治里|本地治里]]的機場，機場有包機航班，附近亦有飛行學校。本地治里市政府在2010年代初決定擴充機場，以容納大型飛機並及興建新航廈<ref name= IBN>{{cite news|title=Flight operations await new terminal|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/flight-operations-await-new-terminal/256422-60-118.html|publisher=IBN Live|date=10 May 2012|accessdate=3 July 2012|archive-date=2012-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513121042/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/flight-operations-await-new-terminal/256422-60-118.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新航廈在2013年1月17日開幕，首班抵港機航為[[香料航空|香料航空]]從班加羅爾飛來<ref>{{cite web |title=First flight to Puducherry from Bangalore on January 17 |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/states/tamil-nadu/first-flight-to-puducherry-from-bangalore-on-january-17/article4277106.ece |accessdate=6 January 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130108091338/http://www.thehindu.com/news/states/tamil-nadu/first-flight-to-puducherry-from-bangalore-on-january-17/article4277106.ece |archive-date=2013-01-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==設施==
本地治里機場有一條方向07/25，長1500米寬30米的跑道，[[機坪|停機坪]]面積為100x150米，新航廈在高峰時可處理300名旅客，導航設施包括[[機場信標|機場信標]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Airport website |url=http://www.aai.aero/allAirports/pondicherry_technicalinfo.jsp |accessdate=3 January 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102155608/http://www.aai.aero/allAirports/pondicherry_technicalinfo.jsp |archivedate=2012年1月2日 }}</ref>。2007年6月，本地治里政府與[[印度机场管理局|印度机场管理局]]簽定一份關於擴建機場的[[諒解備忘錄|諒解備忘錄]]。首期工程包括把跑道延長260米，允許ATR等級飛機進行起降<ref>{{cite news |title=Puducherry ropes in Alliance Air to resume flight services to Bangalore from April 14 |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/puducherry/Puducherry-ropes-in-Alliance-Air-to-resume-flight-services-to-Bangalore-from-April-14/articleshow/46766629.cms |publisher=The Times of India |date=1 April 2015 |accessdate=11 July 2014 |archive-date=2015-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403161212/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/puducherry/Puducherry-ropes-in-Alliance-Air-to-resume-flight-services-to-Bangalore-from-April-14/articleshow/46766629.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。。

進行中的第二期工程會把跑道延長1,100米，需要佔用鄰邦[[泰米尔纳德邦|泰米尔纳德]]200英畝土地，以供大型噴射機起降<ref>{{cite news|title=Puducherry airport to go on stream in October|url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2011-09-03/news/30110146_1_puducherry-airport-runway-lawspet|publisher=The Economic Times|date=3 Sep 2011|accessdate=3 January 2012|archive-date=2013-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510041915/http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2011-09-03/news/30110146_1_puducherry-airport-runway-lawspet|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

